      "body": {
        "type": "TextualBody",
        "value": "Now we see a shadow-like creature enter the frame after the woman falls asleep and begins to dream. The character is dressed in all black, almost confusing itself as a nun. The shadow-mirror-creature is also seen here carrying the flower, the same flower that both the shadow of the woman and the woman picked up before the dream started. ",
